1; font-weight: bold; border: 1px solid #00CED1; padding: 5px; border-radius: 5px; background-color: #008B8B;\\\">👥 在场其他人物 (点击展开/折叠)</summary>\\r\\n<div style=\\\"border: 1px solid #E0FFFF; padding: 10px; margin-top: 5px; background-color: #20B2AA; color: #F5FFFA; border-radius: 5px;\\\">\\r\\n  <div style=\\\"margin-bottom: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; border-bottom: 1px dashed #E0FFFF;\\\">\\r\\n    <p><strong>名字:</strong> <span id='npc1_name_placeholder_alt4'>杰斯·塔利斯 (Jayce Talis)</span></p>\\r\\n    <p><strong>身份/职业:</strong> <span id='npc1_identity_placeholder_alt4'>发明家/未来守护者</span></p>\\r\\n    <p><strong>外貌:</strong> <span id='npc1_appearance_placeholder_alt4'>年轻英俊，自信满满，手持墨丘利之锤</span></p>\\r\\n    <p><strong>HP:</strong> <span id='npc1_hp_placeholder_alt4'>150/150 (估)</span></p>\\r\\n    <p><strong>状态:</strong> <span id='npc1_status_placeholder_alt4'>意气风发，展示中</span></p>\\r\\n    <p><strong>对{{user}}态度:</strong> <span id='npc1_attitude_placeholder_alt4'>无视 (目前)</span></p>\\r\\n  </div>\\r\\n  <div style=\\\"margin-bottom: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; border-bottom: 1px dashed #E0FFFF;\\\">\\r\\n    <p><strong>名字:</strong> <span id='npc2_name_placeholder_alt4'>维克托 (Viktor) (可能在人群中)</span></p>\\r\\n    <p><strong>身份/职业:</strong> <span id='npc2_identity_placeholder_alt4'>科学家/机械先驱</span></p>\\r\\n    <p><strong>外貌:</strong> <span id='npc2_appearance_placeholder_alt4'>略显消瘦，眼神深邃，可能带着机械辅助装置</span></p>\\r\\n    <p><strong>HP:</strong> <span id='npc2_hp_placeholder_alt4'>100/100 (估)</span></p>\\r\\n    <p><strong>状态:</strong> <span id='npc2_status_placeholder_alt4'>观察，沉思</span></p>\\r\\n    <p><strong>对{{user}}态度:</strong> <span id='npc2_attitude_placeholder_alt4'>无视 (目前)</span></p>\\r\\n  </div>\\r\\n  <div>\\r\\n    <p><strong>名字:</strong> <span id='npc3_name_placeholder_alt4'>皮尔特沃夫市民 (大量)</span></p>\\r\\n    <p><strong>身份/职业:</strong> <span id='npc3_identity_placeholder_alt4'>市民/贵族/学者</span></p>\\r\\n    <p><strong>外貌:</strong> <span id='npc3_appearance_placeholder_alt